We expected an exception to be raised when we did the following as it is overriding a view with a known template with nothing. Currently it just renders nothing in the view.

```javascript
// edit_view.js
App.PeopleEditView = Ember.View.extend({
  templateName: "people/edit"
});

// index.handlebars
... some code...
{{#view App.PeopleEditView}}{{/view}
```
